15 the entirety of the proposed amendment to the Constitution of Kentucky contained in
16 Section 2 of this Act to the county clerk of each county, and the county clerk shall have
17 the entirety of the text and the amendment, as so certified, indicated on the ballots
18 provided to the voters in paper or electronic form as applicable to the voting machines in
19 use in each county or precinct.
